name: Spottie WiFi x illa Da Producer: "Full Set"

metadata.name: Full Set (8-Bit Edition)
metadata.description: "Full Set” is the second NFT song drop out of five total NFT song drops from Spottie’s forthcoming album. Collect and hold a NFT from these five NFT drops to receive a limited edition vinyl pressing of the album. Owners of NFTs from the "Full Set" collection have a limited non-exclusive copyright license to the music that comprises the NFTs they own (please visit www.FullSetLicense.com for complete terms and conditions).
